thread.title: Ancient stolen relics returned to Lebanon

title: Ancient stolen relics returned to Lebanon
text:
Ancient stolen relics returned to Lebanon 12:18am EST - 01:49 
Five ancient sculptures, carved between the fourth and sixth centuries BC, have been finally returned to Lebanon after being stolen in the country's civil war.
